  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase: ORBWEAVE's topological knot coupling through the Aquatic Chain. Drift at 6 voices with maximum diffusion matches the knot topology's structural complexity — both systems add internal voices that relate geometrically. Fathom at Character 0.3 preserves the mid-range knot resonances. Tide in Both mode (tremolo + filter) at 0.18 Hz gives the topological surface a breathing quality — as if the knot itself is inhaling and exhaling. Reef at high density provides the physical anchor for an otherwise weightless topological structure.",
